title: Around the AFC in 48 minutes
itunes:title: Around the AFC in 48 minutes
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- discuss the state of every team in the AFC following the 2015 NFL Draft. Highlights include the Jets' new wide receiver group (18:30), the strength of the Bills' roster (21:35) and if the Colts are building the right way. Plus, find out which AFC West team potentially has the best pass-rushing trio in the league (62:00).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
